  shorttitle   = {Awe Narratives},
  abstract     = {It is necessary to have available a variety of evidence-based resilience practices as we experience life’s stressors including the ongoing {COVID}-19 pandemic. Evoking, experiencing, and reflecting on awe moments by developing and sharing an “awe narrative” are a type of mindfulness technique that can have the potential to help someone flourish, enhance their resilience, and have a positive impact on their overall wellbeing. This paper explores how constructing an awe narrative can assist the individual while also possibly having a positive impact on others.},
